OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,FCrystal Palace fans described the UEFA
OL,7,FConference League final against Rayo
OL,8,FVallecano as the 'stuff of dreams' and
OL,9,Fa moment they never thought they would
OL,10,Fsee.
OL,12,FThe Eagles clinched an historic FA Cup
OL,13,Flast year plus a Community Shield but
OL,14,Fon Wednesday night in Leipzig could
OL,15,Fadd a European trophy if they beat
OL,16,FRayo Vallecano.
OL,18,FSpeaking to ITV News London fans said
OL,19,Fthey were proud of what the team had
OL,20,Fachieved and were ready for the big
OL,21,Fgame.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,F"Some people don't realise that if we
OL,7,Fwin tonight, and it's a big if, we
OL,8,Fthen qualify for the Europa League as
OL,9,Fwell. So we could get double bubble
OL,10,Ffor the price of one. Two for the
OL,11,Fprice of one," said fan Nick Philpott.
OL,13,FNick said the atmosphere in Germany
OL,14,F'celebratory' and thousands of
OL,15,Fsupporters were partying together.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
