FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,FFellow fan Paul Gears said: "It's nice
OL,7,Fto see Vallecano fans and Palace fans
OL,8,Fall having pictures and selfies
OL,9,Ftogether. It's a real celebration out
OL,10,Fthere and it's the first European
OL,11,Ffinal for both teams, so it's a
OL,12,Fmassive deal and everyone's having
OL,13,Fgreat fun.
OL,15,F"It's a sea of red and blue out here.
OL,16,FIt's great to see shirts from all
OL,17,Fsorts of years. You can see palace
OL,18,Ffans who have been fans for years all
OL,19,Fsoaking in the moment."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
