OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,FCaptain Dean Henderson was
OL,7,Finstrumental in Palace's 2025 FA Cup
OL,8,Ftriumph over Manchester City and
OL,9,Fadmitted Wednesday's European final
OL,10,Fplayed on his mind during the final
OL,11,Fstages of the campaign.
OL,13,F"Naturally, you're thinking about it,"
OL,14,Fhe said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,F"Even for the last couple of weeks,
OL,7,Fyou're probably thinking, 'let's try
OL,8,Fand win the final'. It's natural. No
OL,9,Fone speaks about it. No one speaks
OL,10,Fabout it to each other. It's just
OL,11,Fabout your individual battles, isn't
OL,12,Fit?"
OL,14,FDeparting Crystal Palace boss Oliver
OL,15,FGlasner has told his finalists that
OL,16,Fthe best leaving gift they could give
OL,17,Fhim would be the opportunity to watch
OL,18,Fthem in the Europa League next season.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
