OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,FThe Eagles are 90 minutes away from
OL,7,Fturning Glasner's dream into a
OL,8,Freality, with just Rayo Vallecano
OL,9,Fstanding in the way of more titles
OL,10,Funder the Austrian manager, who will
OL,11,Fmark the end of his transformative
OL,12,FCrystal Palace tenure when the final
OL,13,Fwhistle blows at the Red Bull Arena in
OL,14,FLeipzig.
OL,16,FPalace chairman Steve Parish has
OL,17,Fcredited Glasner with taking his club
OL,18,Fto an unprecedented level.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,FAnd Glasner once again challenged the
OL,7,Fsouth Londoners not to place any
OL,8,Flimits on their ambitions.
OL,10,FHe said: "Yesterday they had a nice
OL,11,Ffarewell for me, and then I said a few
OL,12,Fwords. I said that for me, the best
OL,13,Fthing would be, of course, winning
OL,14,Ftomorrow, but not for winning
OL,15,Ftomorrow, but because then they plan
OL,16,FEuropean football in the Europa League
OL,17,Fnext year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,F"They would get next year what we
OL,7,Fshould have gotten this year. Then I
OL,8,Fsaid I would like to watch on TV that
OL,9,Fthey would start their Europa League
OL,10,Fwith the desire and the confidence
OL,11,Fthat they can win the Europa League as
OL,12,Fwell.
OL,14,F"This would make me really happy,
OL,15,Fbecause then I think we created a
OL,16,Fmindset at the end that is always
OL,17,Fsuccessful.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1779948269
OL,3,CCrystal Palace fans on the European
OL,4,Cfinal they never thought they would see
OL,6,F"That doesn't mean that you win a
OL,7,Ftrophy every single year, but at the
OL,8,Fend you will always get the best out
OL,9,Fof every single player and every
OL,10,Fsingle team, and that's why I hope
OL,11,Fthat we win tomorrow, that these
OL,12,Fplayers can play Europa League
OL,13,Ffootball next season."
